 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/28/01 1:57:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of Jiva</span><hr size=1> I can confirm that Draught of Jiva drops in Chardok, that's where I got my copy. Unfortunatly I don't know what dropped it, I was in an AE group at the time and at the end of the pull our cleric happened to loot a copy. <p>I've been cursed by god to wander the earth in an endless quest to conquer man.Light a man a fire, and he will be warm for a day.Light a man on fire, and he will bewarm for the rest of his life. </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uevilrulz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Evilrulz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/1/01 11:05:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of Jiva</span><hr size=1> I know people wont belive me, but a long time ago 6-9 months ago when I was 52 I was tryin to get absond from turn in spells and got Jiva. I remeber specifically gettin this spell cause I thought turn in spells only returned 51-54 spells and at 52 I had just gotten a 55 spell. At the time I was rather upset I had gotten a spell I was so far away from using but I guess I was lucky. I also belive I have seen this drop from reavers cause when it did i was mad that a turn in spell was droppin from mobs like reavers. Its entirely possible it was a bug that was fixed long ago.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/1/01 12:29:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of Jiva</span><hr size=1> It drops in at least 4 or 5 zones.  It is a fairly common spell.  I know for sure it drops in Seb and Skyfire, and a few more zones I don't recall. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uquikpick.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Quikpick</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/1/01 12:50:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of Jiva</span><hr size=1> I got mine in CoM off a Black Reaver. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyaldin111.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yaldin111</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/1/01 11:45:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> what drops it in Skyfire?</span><hr size=1> What in skyfire drops it?  I need to start looking for it soon.<br><br>Yaldin<br>52 Channeler<br>Karana Server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=marcin>Marcin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/2/01 9:44:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>  </span><hr size=1> Howling Stones *RND <p>Marcin Sanitee<br>60th Sorcerer<br><a href="http://www.portice.com/forums">Bertoxxulous</a><br><a href="http://www.prophecyguild.com">Prophecy</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/2/01 10:25:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  </span><hr size=1> I think I got a copy off a mature chroma.  Although it may have been a mature wurm.  Nothing exotic for sure.<br><br>As you know though, drops in SF are much lower than in dungeons, so I wouldn't count on getting a copy solo.  You'd have to get really lucky. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=111.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=111.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=